quran[11{c,v,t}:
2,38,Qulnah bitoo minhaa jamee 'an fa immaa yaatiyannakum minnee hudan faman tabi'a hudaaya falaa khawfun 'alaihim wa laa hum yahza noon
2,39,Wallazeena kafaroo wa kaz zabooo bi aayaatinaa ulaaa'ika Ashaabun Naari hum feehaa khaalidoon�(section 4)
2,40,Yaa Baneee Israaa'eelaz kuroo ni'matiyal lateee an'amtu 'alaikum wa awfoo bi'Ahdeee oofi bi ahdikum wa iyyaaya farhaboon
2,41,Wa aaminoo bimaaa anzaltu musaddiqal limaa ma'akum wa laa takoonooo awwala kaafirim bihee wa laa tashtaroo bi Aayaatee samanan qaleelanw wa iyyaaya fattaqoon
2,42,Wa laa talbisul haqqa bilbaatili wa taktumul haqqa wa antum ta'lamoon
2,43,Wa aqeemus salaata wa aatuz zakaata warka'oo ma'ar raaki'een
2,44,Ataamuroonan naasa bilbirri wa tansawna anfusakum wa antum tatloonal Kitaab; afalaa ta'qiloon
2,45,Wasta'eenoo bissabri was Salaah; wa innahaa lakabee ratun illaa alal khaashi'een
2,46,Allazeena yazunnoona annahum mulaaqoo Rabbihim wa annahum ilaihi raaji'oon�(section 5)
2,47,Yaa Baneee Israaa'eelaz kuroo ni'matiyal lateee an'amtu 'alaikum wa annee faddaltukum 'alal 'aalameen
2,48,Wattaqoo Yawmal laa tajzee nafsun 'an nafsin shai'anw wa laa yuqbalu minhaa shafaa'atunw wa laa yu'khazu minhaa 'adlunw wa laa hum yunsaroon
